  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>Using <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661911\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrCryptomatte</a> workflow, you can output IDs in Katana for easy selection in a compositing application. You can then use that selection as a mask to make changes selectively in post packages.</p><p>PxrCryptomatte is supplied as a <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661887\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sample Filter</a> plugin. As such the output for Cryptomatte is stored as a separate EXR file from your beauty or denoise outputs. Please note an OpenEXR output (file.exr) is required to store the values correctly.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"fc56ed70-73f2-4615-b818-200ab2d17ee1\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>We only render this when using a disk render to avoid overwriting files during an interactive session</p></div></div><p><br/></p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"1167\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179578/cryptomatteKatanaScenegraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531546770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1006&amp;height=782\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546179578/cryptomatteKatanaScenegraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531546770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"782\" data-width=\"1006\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546179596\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"cryptomatteKatanaScenegraph.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546179578\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"cbd1cc75-ac92-48b3-967f-8fd91f264b48\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179578/cryptomatteKatanaScenegraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531546770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1006&amp;height=782 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179578/cryptomatteKatanaScenegraph.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531546770&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1006&amp;height=782 1x\"></span><p style=\"text-align: center;\">The attached example file for Katana workflow.</p><p>This file contains two PxrCryptomatte nodes to output both object and material IDs.</p><p>Example Workflow:</p><ol start=\"1\"><li><p>Create a PxrCryptomatte node. Specify the file name and path. The example file uses a script to write to your Temp directory.</p></li><li><p>Layer: Select the layer type, Name (object) or Material.</p></li><li><p>Connect these to a ShadingNodeArrayConnector</p></li><li><p>Create a PrmanShadingNode and select PxrSampleFilterCombiner. Connect the ShadingNodeArrayConnector.out to the input of this shading node.</p></li><li><p>Create a NetworkMaterial node , right-click and &quot;Add terminal&quot;, select &quot;samplefilter&quot; in the Prman dropdown.</p></li><li><p>Connect the prmanSamplefilter.out to the NetworkMaterial.</p></li><li><p>Merge the above network (easy to reuse) into the trunk.</p></li><li><p>Create a MaterialAssign node and assign the Cryptomatte NetworkMaterial to /root</p></li></ol><p>Render your scene and look for the output EXR in the path you defined above. The example file will output two EXRs, one with Object IDs and another with Material IDs as seen below.</p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"453\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179578/RfK_Crypto_object.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531547032&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=371&amp;height=369\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546179578/RfK_Crypto_object.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531547032&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"369\" data-width=\"371\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546179608\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RfK_Crypto_object.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546179578\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"47993344-2963-41ac-b473-1c6b96dde333\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179578/RfK_Crypto_object.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531547032&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=371&amp;height=369 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179578/RfK_Crypto_object.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531547032&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=371&amp;height=369 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"453\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179578/RfK_Crypto_material.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531547032&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=370&amp;height=370\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546179578/RfK_Crypto_material.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531547032&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"370\" data-width=\"370\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546179605\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RfK_Crypto_material.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546179578\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6ed58e2b-5a1f-4323-83ec-8d303014f42e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179578/RfK_Crypto_material.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531547032&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=370&amp;height=370 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546179578/RfK_Crypto_material.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531547032&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=370&amp;height=370 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p>You can download the above scene created in Katana 2.6 v4 as <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/20218736/cryptomatte_filters.katana?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1694037891069&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" rel=\"nofollow\">cryptomatte_filters.katana</a></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
    }
